      <h1>Forskrift om adgang til &#xE5; unnta for l&#xF8;nnsplikt og utvide dagpengeperioden innen visse n&#xE6;ringer.</h1>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapI" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2003-07-16-963/KAPITTEL_1">
        <h2 data-text-align="center">I</h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">I f&#xF8;lgende n&#xE6;ringer kan arbeidsgiver permittere i inntil 42 uker i l&#xF8;pet av de siste 18 m&#xE5;neder f&#xF8;r l&#xF8;nnsplikten gjeninntrer:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Verkstedsindustrien, verftsindustri, on- og offshore</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Prosessindustrien</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Bygg- og anleggsn&#xE6;ringen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Skogbruk- og treforedlingsindustri</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Hotell- og restaurantn&#xE6;ringen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">Reiselivsn&#xE6;ringen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">IT-n&#xE6;ringen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-8"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-8-ledd-1">Grafisk industri</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-9"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-9-ledd-1">Tekstil- og bekledningsindustrien</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-10"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-10-ledd-1">M&#xF8;belindustrien</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-11"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-11-ledd-1">N&#xE6;ringsmiddelindustrien.</article></article></li></ul></article>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2">Det kan ytes dagpenger til de permitterte i samme periode som nevnt i f&#xF8;rste ledd.</article>
      </section>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapII" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2003-07-16-963/KAPITTEL_2">
